<div class='flex-box columns'><section class='column box-cell new-stories waypoint column1' data-fixselector='header.fixable' data-key='new' id='column-new'><h1 class='semantic'>The New Stuff</h1>
<div class='column-content'><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/09/17/meetup-12-year-anniversary-heiferman/">12 Years on, Meetup Still Envisions Powerful Communities</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>James O'Brien</span></h2><time datetime="Wed, 17 Sep 2014 11:15:08 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>Meetup has survived where others haven't, and it's staked out a space all its own as a major, if somewhat atypical, player in the social-network milieu.</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/09/09/apple-live-hub-social/">Apple Finally Gets Social With Its Own &#x27;Live Hub&#x27; for iPhone Event</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Christina Warren</span></h2><time datetime="Tue, 09 Sep 2014 16:54:20 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>The notoriously closed-off company has put together a full #AppleLive social hub.</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/08/28/mashies-late-entry-deadline/">Mashies Late-Entry Deadline Extended to September 5</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Marian Barrett</span></h2><time datetime="Thu, 28 Aug 2014 19:23:34 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>Submit your best work in digital marketing, advertising and social to the Mashies by Friday, Sept. 5.</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/08/26/how-to-get-a-job-using-social-media-class/">Learning How to Score a Job Using Social Media, for Beginners</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Sheffie Elencweig</span></h2><time datetime="Tue, 26 Aug 2014 15:09:15 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>Mashable is collaborating with The Muse to bring you a free, email-based class series called How to Get a Job Using Social Media.</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/08/26/social-good-summit-jimmy-carter/">Jimmy Carter Talks Preventable Disease at Social Good Summit 2014</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Marian Barrett</span></h2><time datetime="Tue, 26 Aug 2014 14:25:14 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>Former U.S. President Jimmy Carter will join the Social Good Summit this year via a special video message. Also the founder of The Carter Center, President Carter will speak about the ways social media is helping the eradication of six preventable di...</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/08/12/food-art-vine-results/">These Delectable Food Art Vines Are Top Notch, So Come Hungry</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Annie Park</span></h2><time datetime="Tue, 12 Aug 2014 15:47:03 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>You don't have to be a chef to create a delightful dish. This week, we saw incredible food art by artists and animators on Vine. We partnered with MasterCard for our latest Mashable Vine Challenge. You were asked to come up with creative ways to illu...</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/08/11/content-marketing-roi-data/">61% of Consumers Prefer Companies With Custom Online Content</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Kyli Singh</span></h2><time datetime="Mon, 11 Aug 2014 10:04:32 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>Only 27% of marketers track content metrics effectively. This infographic can help you organize your content marketing goals and make strategic decisions.</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/08/06/facebook-mentions-mashable-minute/">Famous People: Facebook&#x27;s New Elite</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Mashable Video</span></h2><time datetime="Wed, 06 Aug 2014 14:33:02 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>Being famous is awesome -- especially if you're on Facebook. Elliott Morgan weighs in on Facebook's exclusive app for celebrities like Kim Kardashian and Whoopi Goldberg.</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/07/25/mashable-vine-milestone/">Thanks for Helping Us Hit a Vine Milestone</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Jeff Petriello</span></h2><time datetime="Fri, 25 Jul 2014 16:42:27 -0400"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>It's been an incredible journey, and we're constantly inspired by the incredible talent on the platform.</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/07/18/the-emojis-are-living-among-us/">Warning: The Emoji Live Among Us</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Dennis Green</span></h2><time datetime="Fri, 18 Jul 2014 17:05:05 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>The poop emoji looks way too happy on that swing set.</p></article></div></section><section class='column box-cell hot-stories waypoint column2' data-fixselector='header.fixable' data-key='rising' id='column-rising'><h1 class='semantic'>The Next Big Thing</h1>
<div class='column-content'><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/09/24/vine-update-vine-challenge/">Vine Challenge: Use the Newest Update to Create Cool Six-Second Videos</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Annie Park</span></h2><time datetime="Thu, 25 Sep 2014 03:25:16 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>Vine's newest update includes the ability to upload videos and edit frames, as well as use an accurate level and flashlight. </p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/09/20/social-good-summit-2014-online/">How to Follow Social Good Summit 2014 Online</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>MJ Franklin</span></h2><time datetime="Sat, 20 Sep 2014 16:30:52 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>Social Good Summit is back! On Sunday, Sept. 21 and Monday, Sept. 22, advocates from across the globe are coming together to discuss some of the biggest challenges our world is facing. Whether it's at local Meetups or at the main stage event at the 9...</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/09/12/off-the-page-vine-challenge-results/">6 Vines That Bring Stories and Doodles to Life</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Annie Park</span></h2><time datetime="Fri, 12 Sep 2014 20:30:31 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>Canadian artists Daniel Lynds and Sundi Richard guest-hosted last week's challenge; take a look at their picks.</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/09/09/fashion-rocks-tweets-design-dress/">Verizon Turning Your &#x27;Fashion Rocks&#x27; Tweets Into an Outfit</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Brian Anthony Hernandez</span></h2><time datetime="Tue, 09 Sep 2014 22:28:50 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>This is a real-time garment, with tweets about Fashion Rocks' music and fashion influencing the pattern and color of the final design. </p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/09/03/kc-james-visits-mashable/">Vine Star KC James Makes 6-Second Comedy Sketches His Career</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Annie Park</span></h2><time datetime="Thu, 04 Sep 2014 02:24:38 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>Who says six seconds can't make a career? Vine comedian KC James stopped by 'Mashable' HQ to tell us about his rise to fame on the video-sharing platform.</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/09/02/guilty-celebrity-nood-fappers-prostate-cancer/">Reddit Users Get Remorse Over Nude Pictures, Try Donating to Charity</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Brian Koerber</span></h2><time datetime="Tue, 02 Sep 2014 20:58:26 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>No money can fix this breach of privacy. </p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/08/29/360-vine-challenge-results/">8 Vines That Will Make Your Head Spin 360 Degrees</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Annie Park</span></h2><time datetime="Fri, 29 Aug 2014 17:24:52 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>We partnered with Hewlett-Packard for this week's Vine challenge, themed around 360 degrees. Watch our favorites here -- but careful, you might get dizzy!</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/08/22/360-vine-challenge/">Vine Challenge: Capture Objects in 360 Degrees</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Annie Park</span></h2><time datetime="Fri, 22 Aug 2014 17:26:57 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>The tech of our days is so advanced that it's fair to say we've got everything we need. From smartphones and tablets of all sizes to bendable TVs and Bluetooth padlocks, nearly every gadget has multiple things to show off, appearance- and function-wi...</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/08/21/transformation-vine-challenge-roundup/">8 Vines of Transformations Happening Before Your Very Eyes</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Annie Park</span></h2><time datetime="Thu, 21 Aug 2014 13:46:00 -0400"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>We asked you to create tricky transformations for our latest Vine challenge. Here are our favorite submissions.</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/08/17/instagram-famous-photographers/">8 Famous Photographers Worth Following on Instagram</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Yohana Desta</span></h2><time datetime="Sun, 17 Aug 2014 12:03:50 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>Class up your Instagram feed by following some real photographers.</p></article></div></section><section class='column box-cell big-stories waypoint column3' data-fixselector='header.fixable' data-key='hot' id='column-hot'><h1 class='semantic'>What's Hot</h1>
<div class='column-content'><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/09/27/google-doodle-16th-birthday/">Google Doodle Celebrates Its 16th Birthday</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Chelsea Stark</span></h2><time datetime="Sat, 27 Sep 2014 18:56:07 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>Happy sweet 16, Google Doodle!
</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/09/26/ello-facebook/">If Not Ello, Something Else: Facebook&#x27;s &#x27;Real Names&#x27; Policy Could Turn It Into Friendster</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Chris Taylor</span></h2><time datetime="Fri, 26 Sep 2014 22:42:41 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>The Ello rebellion may be short-lived, or the tiny startup that created it may indeed be the Facebook killer that gives Zuckerberg nightmares.</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/09/26/ello-founder-talks-facebook-business/">Ello Cofounder Doesn&#x27;t Think Facebook Is a Social Network</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Karissa Bell</span></h2><time datetime="Sat, 27 Sep 2014 01:49:37 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>Ello cofounder Paul Budnitz on what's next for the anti-Facebook and how the private social network can turn a profit without advertising.</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/09/25/whats-the-deal-with-ello/">What&#x27;s Up With Ello, the Anti-Facebook Social Network?</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Karissa Bell</span></h2><time datetime="Fri, 26 Sep 2014 02:25:25 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>The bizarreness that is Ello.</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/09/25/hyperlapse-selfie/">How to Snap the Perfect Hyperlapse Selfie</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Kyli Singh</span></h2><time datetime="Thu, 25 Sep 2014 21:35:24 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>Selfies just got a whole lot fancier. Here's how to snap a great Hyperlapse selfie, dubbed &quot;selfielapse.&quot;</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/09/25/instagram-hyperlapse-selfies/">Time-Lapse Selfies Are Now a Thing, Courtesy of Instagram&#x27;s Hyperlapse</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Karissa Bell</span></h2><time datetime="Thu, 25 Sep 2014 18:12:53 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>The selfielapses are coming.</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/09/24/amazon-wish-list-hashtag/">You Can Now Add Items to Your Amazon Wish List With a Tweet</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Karissa Bell</span></h2><time datetime="Thu, 25 Sep 2014 00:39:30 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>Amazon revealed a new shopping hashtag Wednesday that allows shoppers to automatically add items to their wish list with a tweet.</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/09/24/apple-ios-8-twitter-reaction/">The Collective Twitter Freakout That Was the iOS 8.0.1 Update</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Rex Santus</span></h2><time datetime="Wed, 24 Sep 2014 20:59:36 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>Cue the witty banter.</p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/09/23/2030-photo-challenge-roundup/">Things We Still Want to See in the Year 2030</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Annie Park</span></h2><time datetime="Wed, 24 Sep 2014 03:30:54 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>From flowers and bees to newspapers and ancient architecture, we saw a wide variety of submissions. </p></article><article class="flat"><header><hgroup><h1><a href="http://mashable.com/2014/09/22/twitter-app-how-to-find-drafts/">How to Find Your Drafts and Lists in Twitter&#x27;s New iPhone App</a></h1><h2><span class='byline-meta'>Written by</span> <span class='byline-author'>Karissa Bell</span></h2><time datetime="Mon, 22 Sep 2014 23:32:56 +0000"><post class="post_date rfc2822"></post></time></hgroup></header><p>How to find your drafts and lists in Twitter's new iPhone app.</p></article></div></section></div>
