That Will Make Your Head Spin 360 Degrees\n\nOne Vine celebrity, KC James, recently stopped by Mashable's New York office. In just a year and a half, James has turned a fun hobby into a full-fledged career, with more than 4 million followers on the platform. \n\nHe's well known for his series of comedy sketches, many of which involve getting hit in the face by random objects. Honest, creative and fearless, James has made a name for himself as master of capturing comedic slices of everyday situations.\n\nWe shot several Vines with James while he was at our headquarters. As expected, he was a natural comedian, and one that gave 110% of his voice, energy and whimsical humor to perfecting a video. \n\nIf you haven't already, watch the video, above, to see our interview with James, as well as behind-the-scenes footage of the making of the Vines.\n\nHave something to add to this story? Share it in the comments."},"shares":{"twitter":938,"facebook":395,"google_plus":26,"linked_in":69,"pinterest":1,"total":1429},"comments_count":0,"image":"http://rack.0.mshcdn.com/media/ZgkyMDE0LzA5LzA0LzMyL0tDX0phbWVzLjdlYjE1LmpwZwpwCXRodW1iCTk1MHg1MzQjCmUJanBn/509ff94f/a04/KC_James.jpg","responsive_images":[{"image":"http://rack.0.mshcdn.com/media/ZgkyMDE0LzA5LzA0LzMyL0tDX0phbWVzLjdlYjE1LmpwZwpwCXRodW1iCTM1NngyMDUjCmUJanBn/08790fb0/a04/KC_James.jpg","query":true,"size":"356x205#"},{"image":"http://rack.0.mshcdn.com/media/ZgkyMDE0LzA5LzA0LzMyL0tDX0phbWVzLjdlYjE1LmpwZwpwCXRodW1iCTcxMng0MTAjCmUJanBn/438114a3/a04/KC_James.jpg","query":"(min-resolution: 1.5dppx)","size":"712x410#"},{"image":"http://rack.2.mshcdn.com/media/ZgkyMDE0LzA5LzA0LzMyL0tDX0phbWVzLjdlYjE1LmpwZwpwCXRodW1iCTI4MHgxNTcjCmUJanBn/f7c188ce/a04/KC_James.jpg","query":"(max-width: 480px)","size":"280x157#"},{"image":"http://rack.0.mshcdn.com/media/ZgkyMDE0LzA5LzA0LzMyL0tDX0phbWVzLjdlYjE1LmpwZwpwCXRodW1iCTU2MHgzMTQjCmUJanBn/b6e6401d/a04/KC_James.jpg","query":"(max-width: 480px) and (min-resolution: 1.5dppx)","size":"560x314#"}],"short_url":"http://on.mash.to/1oDKnXS","choice":false,"spotlight":false,"shortcode_data":{"see_also":[{"data-url":"http://mashable.com/2014/08/29/360-vine-challenge-results/"}],"wp_shortcode_manager":[{}]},"velocity":[829,821,814,806,798,790,781,774,766,766,759,744,737,730,722,714,707,700,693,678,671,664,658,651,646,640,634,629,624,618,612,606,600,594,587,581,575,569,564,558,553,548,536,534,525,523,522,520,519,518],"show_sponsorship":true,"channel":"Social Media","channel_link":"http://mashable.com/social-media/"},{"_id":"54062f7b12d2cd65e9000090","id":"2014/09/02/guilty-celebrity-nood-fappers-prostate-cancer","title":"Reddit Users Get Remorse Over Nude Pictures, Try Donating to Charity","title_tag":null,"author":"Brian Koerber","post_date":"2014-09-02T20:58:26+00:00","post_date_rfc":"Tue, 02 Sep 2014 20:58:26 +0000","sort_key":"1xoVSS","link":"http://mashable.com/2014/09/02/guilty-celebrity-nood-fappers-prostate-cancer/","content":{"plain":"UPDATE, September, 3, 1:32 p.m. ET: Water.org has shut down the charity page referenced below but was not immediately available for comment.\n\nUPDATE, September, 3, 11:28 a.m. ET: Reddit users have now started donating to Water.org, a non-profit that provides safe drinking water to those in need.\n\nUPDATE, 5:32 p.m. ET: The Prostate Cancer Foundation has shut down the charity page referenced below and released the following statement:\n\nA post appeared on Reddit late Monday afternoon, September 1, 2014. A Reddit user directed other Reddit users to make a donation to the Prostate Cancer Foundation without the Foundation\u2019s knowledge. We would never condone raising funds for cancer research in this manner. Out of respect for everyone involved and in keeping with our own standards, we are returning all donations that resulted from this post.\n\nRemorseful Redditors are attempting to absolve their guilty consciences over looking at leaked photos of celebrities -- by donating to prostate cancer research, allegedly because \"Jennifer Lawrence has donated to help cure prostate cancer.\"\n\nSo far more than $6,000 has been donated by Reddit users to the Prostate Cancer Foundation -- despite the fact that the Prostate Cancer Foundation isn't actually listed as one of Jennifer Lawrence's  supported charities.\n\nSee also: The FBI Is Now Involved in Hunt for the Celebrity Nude Photo Hacker\n\nHundreds of nude photographs of more than a dozen celebrities spread across the Internet, quickly making their way from their origins on 4chan and the anonymous image board anon-ib to more mainstream message boards such as Reddit.\n\nShortly after the breach was exposed, a subreddit called \"TheFappening\" was created. (\"Fap\" is a word for masturbation commonly used on Reddit.) As new photos were released, a live post provided updates, and a leaked photo archive compiled the photos.\n\nThe live thread has since been banned; the archive post is \"no longer available due to a copyright claim.\"\n\nLeaked photos are being removed from imgur and other hosting services as quickly as possible -- but not fast enough. The mod post attatched to the top of the subreddit lists over 50 \"whitelisted\" image hosting domains.\n\nIf you're casually browsing Reddit, you won't notice any threads from TheFappening; it was removed from the main page, r/all, per the suggestion of the subreddit's admins. Still, according to user johnsmcjohn, a moderator for TheFappening, the subreddit has seen 12,187,720 unique visitors in 3 days.\n\nAccording to one anonymous post discussing a 4chan thread, a celebrity porn exchange ring has been going on for years. One redditor even points out that dicussions on anon-ib have been surrounding stolen celebrity photos \"more or less dedicated to ripping iCloud accounts.\"\n\nRegardless of the origins of the pictures, the fact that the donations were returned appears to have been a sobering moment for at least one Redditor:\r\nReddit responds to having its sticky money rejected by the Prostate Cancer Foundation: pic.twitter.com/tmvI1QUPJV\n\n\u2014 Neetzan Zimmerman (@neetzan) September 2, 2014\n\n[H/T: The Daily Dot]"},"shares":{"facebook":151,"twitter":1038,"linked_in":57,"google_plus":68,"pinterest":1,"total":1315},"comments_count":0,"image":"http://rack.3.mshcdn.com/media/ZgkyMDE0LzA5LzAzL2E5L01vbmV5LmYxYzlkLmpwZwpwCXRodW1iCTk1MHg1MzQjCmUJanBn/0167486f/a2d/Money.jpg","responsive_images":[{"image":"http://rack.3.mshcdn.com/media/ZgkyMDE0LzA5LzAzL2E5L01vbmV5LmYxYzlkLmpwZwpwCXRodW1iCTM1NngyMDUjCmUJanBn/58b539ce/a2d/Money.jpg","query":true,"size":"356x205#"},{"image":"http://rack.3.mshcdn.com/media/ZgkyMDE0LzA5LzAzL2E5L01vbmV5LmYxYzlkLmpwZwpwCXRodW1iCTcxMng0MTAjCmUJanBn/fef57ebd/a2d/Money.jpg","query":"(min-resolution: 1.5dppx)","size":"712x410#"},{"image":"http://rack.2.mshcdn.com/media/ZgkyMDE0LzA5LzAzL2E5L01vbmV5LmYxYzlkLmpwZwpwCXRodW1iCTI4MHgxNTcjCmUJanBn/6bbded71/a2d/Money.jpg","query":"(max-width: 480px)","size":"280x157#"},{"image":"http://rack.2.mshcdn.com/media/ZgkyMDE0LzA5LzAzL2E5L01vbmV5LmYxYzlkLmpwZwpwCXRodW1iCTU2MHgzMTQjCmUJanBn/7cf9f1e7/a2d/Money.jpg","query":"(max-width: 480px) and (min-resolution: 1.5dppx)","size":"560x314#"}],"short_url":"http://on.mash.to/1lGCLcA","choice":false,"spotlight":false,"shortcode_data":{"see_also":[{"data-slug":"fbi-celebrity-photo-hack"}]},"velocity":[991,994,995,997,999,999,999,998,996,993,1000,995,981,977,973,964,960,956,951,946,941,935,919,913,906,899,892,885,877,869,861,852,844,835,826,818,809,801,792,784,776,768,751,744,727,720,712,705,698,691],"show_sponsorship":true,"channel":"Social Media","channel_link":"http://mashable.com/social-media/"},{"_id":"5400b76d12d2cd6d930011cd","id":"2014/08/29/360-vine-challenge-results","title":"8 Vines That Will Make Your Head Spin 360 Degrees","title_tag":null,"author":"Annie Park","post_date":"2014-08-29T17:24:52+00:00","post_date_rfc":"Fri, 29 Aug 2014 17:24:52 +0000","sort_key":"1xnqy2","link":"http://mashable.com/2014/08/29/360-vine-challenge-results/","content":